方法详细信息

resolver_getRecord

org.xbill.DNS.NAPTRRecord resolver_getRecord(java.lang.String name,
                                             java.lang.String sever_addr)
Resolve the domain name to get the regexp field of the NAPTR record, maybe there are several NAPTR records related to the domain name, select the proper one.

参数：
name - the domain name to resolve
sever_addr - the sever address�� may be used for SID of RID query
返回：
the content of the regexp field of the resolved NAPTR record

resolver_getNAPTRRecords

java.util.Vector<org.xbill.DNS.NAPTRRecord> resolver_getNAPTRRecords(java.lang.String name,
                                                                     java.lang.String severaddr)
Resolve the domain name to get the related NAPTR records, maybe there are several records, get all of them.

参数：
name - the domain name to resolve
返回：
all the related NAPTR records

resolver_selectNAPTRRecord

org.xbill.DNS.NAPTRRecord resolver_selectNAPTRRecord(java.util.Vector<org.xbill.DNS.NAPTRRecord> records)
Select the most proper records among all the related records and return the content of the regexp field of the record.

参数：
records - all the NAPTR records related to one domain name
返回：
the content of the regexp field of the most proper NAPTR record
